2011-09-08T10:57:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/billionton-syste-july-sales-fall-8-39-table-6172-tt.html
BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in July fell 8.39% to NT$33,007,000 from NT$36,029,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  7/2011           7/2010
Sales             33,007           36,029    
YOY%              -8.39%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            202,581          368,930    
YOY%             -45.09% 
=================================================================
 